<plot>Inspired by real events, FLIGHTS OF FANCY is a fish-out-of-water drama with comedic overtones that tells the life story of Lalo Saca, a man who yearns to become a doctor since early childhood and who has to overcome many obstacles (including profound loneliness, culture shock, learning a new language, and surviving a failed marriage) in order to achieve his lifelong dream. Through it all, he remains the steadfast supporter of his family back home in El Salvador, putting his younger brother, Tony, through school. Today, that younger brother is Salvadoran President Tony Saca.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?197733</url></doc>
